AC   Q42093; O22449; O24526; O48907; O48908; O64590;
Multidrug resistance-associated protein 2 (EC 3.6.3.44) (Glutathione
S-conjugate-transporting ATPase 2) (ATP-energized glutathione S-
conjugate pump 2).
